callToAction: NSLOCTEXT("", "BCBBD5794EB5E829FFE4058B0886C3D9", "Discover the cause of the unquiet dead haunting Oakenbane Keep")
description: NSLOCTEXT("", "B71808EE4A64BB3D058D85ADEEE47F75", "Oakenbane Keep was once a proud Kaelar tradition that reached back to the days of the founding of the Aelan Empire. What was once a foremost academy for promising recruits to learn from their venerable forebears is now a ruin filled with wandering shades. We have no explanation for these unquiet dead, but Ryland Hawkens, a military historian, assumes they suffer in this state. He\'s asked me to find the source of the haunting and put their spirits to rest.")
name: MAQ_0013_TheyDeservedBetter
